{
 "name": "RPlog_Escape_from_Caspar",
 "title": "Escape from Caspar",
 "summary": "Battered survivors of a clash with the Sith, the Jedi pilot Leo and the wounded young girl Gabi, daughter of Ambrosia, reach the edge of a remote Imperial TIE airbase outside Orleanon on Caspar, intent on stealing the modified TIE Avenger that is their ride to freedom. While the Imperial commander Amylynn frets over the base's shoddy operations, Leo's CDU veteran allies create a guerrilla distraction with blaster fire and forest fires, drawing the stormtroopers and pilots away. Leo cuts through the fence and, using the Force-enhanced speed and his knowledge of Imperial patrol patterns, carries the feverish, terrified Gabi to the prized fighter, slicing open its hatch and powering up its shields and engines. Amylynn realizes too late that Darth Venger's personal TIE is being stolen by the very Jedi and child she was hunting, scrambling Alpha wing in pursuit. Leo, drawing on his StarOps experience, blasts off and breaks atmosphere ahead of the fighters, the exhausted Gabi clinging to him in fevered prayer as they barrel into space toward the final obstacle between them and freedom.",
